---
import MainLayout from '../../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---
<MainLayout title="High School Sports Banquet Decoration Ideas" description="Creative decoration ideas for high school sports banquets, senior nights, and athletic celebrations. Table decor, centerpieces, banners, and budget-friendly DIY options.">
  <div class="breadcrumbs">
    <div class="container">
      <a href="/">Home</a> <span>/</span> <strong>Decoration Ideas</strong>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>High School Sports Celebration Decoration Ideas</h1>
      <p>Decorations transform a room into a celebration. The right setup makes athletes feel honored and creates beautiful memories.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="page-wrapper">
        <h2>The Centerpiece: Your Table's Anchor</h2>
        <p>Centerpieces are the most visible decoration element at any banquet. They're at eye level throughout dinner, appear in every guest photo, and are often the element guests remember most.</p>
        <p>Options range from simple DIY projects to professional custom pieces. Whatever you choose, go tall enough to be visible above the table but not so tall that guests can't see across the table.</p>

        <h3>Sports Centerpieces — Available by Sport</h3>
        <div class="card-grid">
          <div class="card" style="padding:1rem;">
            <h3>🏈 Football</h3>
            <p>8.75", 11.5", and 12" options</p>
            <a href="https://lakeshore-gift.myshopify.com/products/football-graduation-centerpiece-8-3-4-football" class="card-link" target="_blank">View →</a>
          </div>
          <div class="card" style="padding:1rem;">
            <h3>🏀 Basketball</h3>
            <p>7" and 9" with personalization</p>
            <a href="https://lakeshore-gift.myshopify.com/products/basketball-banquet-table-centerpiece-7-ball" class="card-link" target="_blank">View →</a>
          </div>
          <div class="card" style="padding:1rem;">
            <h3>⚽ Soccer</h3>
            <p>8" custom soccer ball</p>
            <a href="https://lakeshore-gift.myshopify.com/products/custom-soccer-ball-centerpiece-8-soccer-ball-graduation-party-birthday" class="card-link" target="_blank">View →</a>
          </div>
          <div class="card" style="padding:1rem;">
            <h3>🏐 Volleyball</h3>
            <p>8" with team colors</p>
            <a href="https://lakeshore-gift.myshopify.com/products/volleyball-banquet-table-centerpiece-8-volleyball" class="card-link" target="_blank">View →</a>
          </div>
          <div class="card" style="padding:1rem;">
            <h3>📣 Cheerleading</h3>
            <p>Megaphones & pom poms</p>
            <a href="https://lakeshore-gift.myshopify.com/products/cheerleader-megaphone-cheer-banquet-table-centerpiece-cheerleading" class="card-link" target="_blank">View →</a>
          </div>
          <div class="card" style="padding:1rem;">
            <h3>🏃 Track & Field</h3>
            <p>Shoes, hurdles, jumps, javelin</p>
            <a href="https://lakeshore-gift.myshopify.com/products/flying-track-shoe-track-shoe-with-wings-banquet-table-centerpiece" class="card-link" target="_blank">View →</a>
          </div>
          <div class="card" style="padding:1rem;">
            <h3>🏒 Hockey</h3>
            <p>Player outline & puck displays</p>
            <a href="https://lakeshore-gift.myshopify.com/products/hockey-player-centerpiece-unique-jagged-edge-outline-3d-printed-sports-display-8" class="card-link" target="_blank">View →</a>
          </div>
          <div class="card" style="padding:1rem;">
            <h3>🥍 Lacrosse</h3>
            <p>Personalized centerpieces</p>
            <a href="https://lakeshore-gift.myshopify.com/products/other-example-product-2" class="card-link" target="_blank">View →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2>DIY Decoration Projects (Under $50)</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Photo Collage Centerpieces</strong> — Print action shots and arrange in team-color frames</li>
          <li><strong>Painted Sports Equipment</strong> — Spray paint old balls or equipment in school colors</li>
          <li><strong>Team Banner Wall</strong> — Fabric banners in team colors with the program logo</li>
          <li><strong>Memory Jars</strong> — Mason jars filled with team-color candies and a photo</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Budget Decoration Ideas (Under $200 Total)</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Team-color tablecloths from party supply stores ($20-40)</li>
          <li>DIY photo wall with string lights and clips ($15-25)</li>
          <li>Fabric bunting in school colors ($10-15)</li>
          <li>Centerpieces: 1 custom 3D piece per table + simple candles ($50-100)</li>
          <li>Balloon arches in team colors ($20-30)</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Photo Walls & Memory Displays</h2>
        <p>Create a dedicated photo area with a team-branded backdrop, good lighting, and props. Include a timeline wall showing the season's journey — first practice, biggest wins, team celebrations, and final game. This becomes the most popular spot at the event.</p>

        <p><a href="/checklist/" class="btn btn-outline">Get the Banquet Checklist →</a></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>

